    "# DRY\n",
    "- Don't \n",
    "- Repeat\n",
    "- Yourself\n",
    "Principle. Code Smell( fruit gets spoiled you get a pungent smell):(It could be better)\n",
    " - whenever you see logic repeated = code smell\n",
    " - if not DRY -> ROOM FOR IMPROVEMENT IN CODE"
